{"type": "article", "id": 8601, "title": "可卷曲灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-17T07:27:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235151ZRMX0nj14PVceOkm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t巴黎设计工作室 Bina Baitels 为我们带来了一款可以自由卷曲的灯具，它用一个可以翻转的皮革保护套，把发光薄片包在里面，看上去有点像 iPad 的 Smart Cover ，通过调整，使用者可以为自己制造不同的照明环境，既可以作为落地灯出现，又能担任吊灯，壁灯或是台灯。这个系列灯具将会在 2015 年米兰设计周进行展出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235148cqNfXsSWhAP9JuvI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.69437653\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052351482WIYMH7fwbZ95jtl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.94376528\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235149ZQmrLVk6sKwdEevq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.25550122\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235149k8dFfQwny9aoEZIs.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.94865526\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235150I21RpzC8TmxqfH5W.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.84352078\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235150WuUnc9DB6b5ahKE8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235150Cfum9Sn8UWldGpxQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70782396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}